{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2018}} {{Use Australian English|date=June 2018}} {{Infobox V8 Supercar race report | flag = South Australia | title = 2018 The Bend SuperSprint | round_no = 11 | season_no = 16 | year = 2018 | series = SC | track_map = | date = 24–26 August | location = [[Tailem Bend]], [[South Australia]] | circuit = The Bend Motorsport Park | weather = | race1_laps = 24 | race1_dist = 118.808 | pole1 = {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Jamie Whincup]] | pole1_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | pole1_time = 1:50.1371 | winner1 = {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Shane van Gisbergen]] | winner1_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | winner1_time = 48:23.2330 | race2_laps = 41 | race2_dist = 202.964 | pole2 = {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Jamie Whincup]] | pole2_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | pole2_time = 1:48.6498 | winner2 = {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Jamie Whincup]] | winner2_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | winner2_time = 1:17:54.3861 }} The '''2018 The Bend SuperSprint''' (formally known as the '''2018 OTR SuperSprint at The Bend Motorsport Park''')<ref>https://www.speedcafe.com/2018/06/26/the-bend-reveals-supercars-event-sponsor/</ref> was a [[auto racing|motor racing]] event for [[Supercars Championship|Supercars]], held on the weekend of 24–26 August 2018. The event was held at [[The Bend Motorsport Park]] near [[Tailem Bend]] in [[South Australia]] and was the first Supercars event to be held at the circuit. It was the eleventh round of sixteen in the [[2018 Supercars Championship]] and hosted Races 22 and 23 of the season.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.speedcafe.com/2017/10/04/supercars-reveals-16-event-2018-calendar/|title=Supercars reveals 16 event 2018 calendar|work=speedcafe.com|date=4 October 2017|accessdate=4 October 2017}}</ref> The round was open to wildcard entries from the [[Super2 Series]] and saw the grid expanded to twenty-eight cars with the addition of two extra entries.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.supercars.com/news/championship/us-throwback-for-kostecki-wildcard/|title=US throwback for Kostescki wildcard|work=[[Supercars Championship|supercars.com]]|publisher=[[Supercars Championship]]|date=27 June 2018|accessdate=27 June 2018}}</ref>
